name: Renee Mari
who_you_serve: Individuals seeking personal transformation and growth.
what_you_do: Renee Marie is an embodied leadership mentor, speaker, and nervous-system-informed guide for women who are already successful but know their next level requires a different way of leading.
social_proof: Featured in New York Business Now, The US Times, Moguls of Business, Stars of Entrepreneurship, and Hustle Weekly.
business_focus: Guiding high-achieving women founders, creatives, and leaders to recalibrate their nervous systems, identity, and leadership so success feels sustainable, grounded, and powerful, not exhausting.
service_provided: Private mentorship, consulting, group experiences, immersions, speaking engagements, workshops, thought leadership, education
